      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass benchmark verification cases relevant to rotating machinery internal flow.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verified against rotating cavity benchmark (Roache 1998) and internal FDA benchmark pump case. Code verification documented in solver validation report VR-2022-CFD-001."
